{"tid":204520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉處指多重加密難解　保安專家：九重加密都無用　籲勿用技術字眼混淆視聽","createTime":"2017-04-17T06:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T14:05:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93df411f3e27f0769986827025e14285286a0d75","tid":204520,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">選舉處指多重加密難解　保安專家拆解：九重加密都無用　籲勿用技術字眼混淆視聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170413/s00001/1492063922766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170413%2Fs00001%2F1492063922766&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bb19c750\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170413%2Fs00001%2F1492063922766&h=b894bc2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170413/s00001/1492063922766</a></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170413/s00001/fbb2917aa24b2134524971f8ef7a2d4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170413%2Fs00001%2Ffbb2917aa24b2134524971f8ef7a2d4e.jpg&h=6f5e70ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （明報製圖／資料圖片／莫乃光facebook片段截圖）</div><br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處在特首選舉後備場地丟失兩部載有378萬名選民資料的手提電腦，引起社會關注，政府事後強調，電腦資料設有多重加密，極難破解，資料外泄風險低。不過有資訊保安專家直言「九重加密都無用」，又認為不應以「高技術字眼」混淆公眾。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處早前遺失的兩部手提電腦，其中一部載有378萬名選民資料，包括姓名、地址及身分證號碼。選舉事務處事務處稱，所有資料已根據相關保安要求進行加密儲存，設有多重加密，極難破解，資料外泄風險相當低。<br />\n<br />\n不過資訊科技界議員莫乃光昨日於facebook上載短片，片中資訊保安專家賴灼東指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">涉事電腦是「備份電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，所有軟件、加密匙都會儲存在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，即使多重加密「好advance好高級」，但與沒有上鎖無分別</span>，「你個密碼同加密匙，同個程式基本上擺埋一齊，就算我話畀你聽用幾多加密，雙重，三重，四重，或者九重加密都無用，即係話你鎖完個櫃，條鎖匙擺喺上面，咁你同無鎖有乜分別啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」<br />\n<br />\n賴灼東批評選舉處做法未符合保安指示，又認為不應用「高技術字眼」混淆視聽。他另提到，場地有32部電腦，當中只有6部載有個人資料，質疑為何賊人剛巧選中上述兩部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n賴灼東提醒選民，要留意近期有否接到可疑電話、信件、電郵，電話會否無故失效等，大廈保安也要加強警覺。他續說，政府絕不能逃避責任及懲處，應徹查是否有人失職。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處總選舉事務主任黃思文前日回應說，手提電腦加密的技術相當高，引述資訊科技總監辦公室稱破解是有難度，當局目前認為資料外泄風險相當低。黃思文又說，上屆特首選舉已曾帶全港選民資料系統到會場，但自己在今次事件前並不知情，指有關做法或因個別員工欠缺警覺性，會在檢討後建議下屆特首選舉不帶備該套系統。"},{"pid":"a33daad371487a8589427b7ea6820bf54b4e5c57","tid":204520,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"冇人需要負責。拉唔到人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475bf983a2302244b4ae6978a177cd9a9400befa","tid":204520,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"港豬: 唔理啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd8052d65681a20ca5e835c7adeb218901b636b","tid":204520,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔理LU"},{"pid":"239b2ee0a78a915f5b0acca032fdb9155c85750f","tid":204520,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"呢d係個別事件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"h