 />\n民事告佢索償又冇乜理據可以證明到有直接損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係咁大件事都唔洗炒人</blockquote><br />\n唔洗落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea51b4de25cdb01f957abc626019e4b133ef36d3","tid":204520,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe18096f93eb77ca49b6d4e1fb9b707994af2ad","tid":204520,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"so<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4dc5b4663526f1b7f72b92a728258b4e9c3117","tid":204520,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人收到唔咸唔淡既廣東話電話問你選擇意向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}